Usage: ctd_win [-help] [-id <string>] [-include_reporting_only_skew_groups]
               [-title <string>] [-unit_delay]

-help                                   # Prints out the command usage
-id <string>                            # Specify unique window ID for the
                                        # opening Clock Tree Debugger window.
                                        # (string, optional)
-include_reporting_only_skew_groups     # Include non-constraining skew groups.
                                        # (bool, optional)
-title <string>                         # Specify the title of Clock Tree
                                        # Debugger window. (string, optional)
-unit_delay                             # Open Clock Tree Debugger window in
                                        # unit delay mode. (bool, optional)